title: Nostradamus - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 9/27/22
itunes:title: Nostradamus - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 9/27/22
description:
George Noory and author John Hogue explore his analysis of the predictions of the 16th century prophet Nostradamus, and how many of his prophesies are coming true today, like the war in Ukraine, the weakening US economy and the Covid pandemic.
